score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1aa9ab6759a95179af04a842117bcb4975323a32","tid":2434764,"uid":138409,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T13:02:51.000Z","msg":"出咗MV<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wJKHQU2GuwY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DwJKHQU2GuwY&d=sOSR1epLEapJbLCvIyWedbXdyKWV89KwSxbYnQ5zRIM%3D&h=48a6db74\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wJKHQU2GuwY</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T13:21:29.000Z","msg":"又係鍾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />雪"},{"pid":"fe573d1c85a0f38bfdae09d4a39c3bb0de4c0a0e","tid":2434764,"uid":138409,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1aa9ab6759a95179af04a842117bcb4975323a32","tid":2434764,"uid":138409,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T13:02:51.000Z","msg":"出咗MV<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wJKHQU2GuwY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DwJKHQU2GuwY&d=sOSR1epLEapJbLCvIyWedbXdyKWV89KwSxbYnQ5zRIM%3D&h=48a6db74\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wJKHQU2GuwY</a>"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T13:44:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wJKHQU2GuwY&amp;lc=UgytsdPvCkNJq0Adhmp4AaABAg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DwJKHQU2GuwY%26lc%3DUgytsdPvCkNJq0Adhmp4AaABAg&d=sOSR1epLEapJbLCvIyWedbXdyKWV89KwSxbYnQ5zRIM%3D&h=f4811cce\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wJKHQU2GuwY&amp;lc=UgytsdPvCkNJq0Adhmp4AaABAg</a><br />\n<br />\n【MV+歌詞 超譯時間】<br />\n<br />\n從前有個女仔，佢嘅生活千篇一律：撳鐘、嘢食遞到埋口，食飽就畀人抽血，榨取資源；然後仲要畀人成日係耳邊洗腦（千祈唔好好似藍鬍子個老婆噉啊，乖乖聽話就可以啦），膜拜某「權威」以及某本「小紅書」，日復如是。<br />\n<br />\n但係即使佢咁虔誠嘅態度可以消除表面嘅痛苦（唔需要擔心搵唔到食，唔需要擔心前路因爲畀人安排好晒，簡直係「烏托邦」）<br />\n佢依然奢想自由，即使聽聞好可怕。（「虔誠能醫好一些痛楚，為何仍奢想風的探訪」）<br />\n<br />\n逐漸地，現實嘅殘酷同血腥  令個女仔清醒過嚟（「無意找到一抹血的痕跡 那種紅色 滲出縫隙 門前有一切挑撥我的神經 渴想無聲 寧願清醒」）<br />\n佢懷疑起一直被灌輸嘅意識形態（「懷疑無盤古之初 懷疑童謠詩歌」）<br />\n無辦法自欺欺人，繼續同樣嘅生活（「如何能重新擁抱你假裝不想說謊 我不是我」）<br />\n<br />\n有一日，女主角終於徹底厭倦被圈養嘅生活；佢決定反抗外界嘅剝削（扯開抽血管），啲血滴咗落本「自古以來神聖不可侵犯」嘅小紅書度，竟然彈咗度傳送門出嚟，令佢無出路嘅生命似乎打破咗一個缺口。<br />\n<br />\n原來佢嘅前路充滿可能性，只喺佢一直以來循規蹈矩 劃地自限（「懷疑無甚麼黑房懷疑無門可鎖原來門前的只有我不敢跨出更多」）<br />\n<br />\n面對再次遞到埋口嘅「飼料」，佢寧願選擇自殘，同本小紅書攬炒。果然，更大嘅傳送門出現咗；但係度門慢慢又縮返細。<br />\n<br />\n個女仔用盡自己嘅血淋落去本書度，趁道逃生門仲開緊嘅時候，離開狹窄單調如豬欄嘅現狀，出走到更寬廣嘅未知遠方。（「原來門前的一抹血歸於新的遠方 更寬廣」）"},{"pid":"48d314cf341efc91aafa136f17a320bd6f4eb224","tid":2434764,"uid":186882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fe573d1c85a0f38bfdae09d4a39c3bb0de4c0a0e","tid":2434764,"uid":138409,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1aa9ab6759a95179af04a842117bcb4975323a32","tid":2434764,"uid":138409,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T13:02:51.000Z","msg":"出咗MV<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wJKHQU2GuwY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DwJKHQU2GuwY&d=sOSR1epLEapJbLCvIyWedbXdyKWV89KwSxbYnQ5zRIM%3D&h=48a6db74\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wJKHQU2GuwY</a>"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T13:44:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wJKHQU2GuwY&amp;lc=UgytsdPvCkNJq0Adhmp4AaABAg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DwJKHQU2GuwY%26lc%3DUgytsdPvCkNJq0Adhmp4AaABAg&d=sOSR1epLEapJbLCvIyWedbXdyKWV89KwSxbYnQ5zRIM%3D&h=f4811cce\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wJKHQU2GuwY&amp;lc=UgytsdPvCkNJq0Adhmp4AaABAg</a><br />\n<br />\n【MV+歌詞 超譯時間】<br />\n<br />\n從前有個女仔，佢嘅生活千篇一律：撳鐘、嘢食遞到埋口，食飽就畀人抽血，榨取資源；然後仲要畀人成日係耳邊洗腦（千祈唔好好似藍鬍子個老婆噉啊，乖乖聽話就可以啦），膜拜某「權威」以及某本「小紅書」，日復如是。<br />\n<br />\n但係即使佢咁虔誠嘅態度可以消除表面嘅痛苦（唔需要擔心搵唔到食，唔需要擔心前